Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:17.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この世界は非現実
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:23.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ただ刷り込まれたビジョン
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}無限遠点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:31.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}価値観を今
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}上書きする　変哲の無い宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}傲慢な神は目に映らない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}光速度で支配続けるならば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:50.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕は　僕だけは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}奇跡的で致命的な
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:57.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}マイノリティでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:58.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I can fly──
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あの瞬間、あの場面が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミにとって特別なら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:09.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}過去は離れて行くものなんかじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}傷つく事の痛みより
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:15.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}大事なシーン　その全ての
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:20.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ヒカリが今ゼロを生む
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}There is no god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Wonderful new world.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------OPCN---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:17.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果当今的天地并非现实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:23.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}仅仅只是一个虚妄的掩饰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:27.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}无限远方那一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:31.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}价值观逐渐畸变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:35.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}逐步重建 不起涟漪宇宙间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}各路诸神心傲慢 藐视万物的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}仍以为光速 还能支配到宇宙天边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:50.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}对是我 只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}是极其罕见的致命异类之种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:57.44,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即将燎遍禁锢的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:58.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}自由翱翔──
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}还是那个瞬间 还是那些画面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:04.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}还是那些留恋 留在你的心间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:09.52,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}过去的那些琐事决未从此消失 也未曾远逝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}过去那些伤痛 再也不要提及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:15.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}回忆那些留恋 是你成长阶梯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:20.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}用回忆的光将零之门 开启
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}从此再无神明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}欢迎美丽新世界
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------EDJP---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:13.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Come to me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:16.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Embrace my tears
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:22.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Let me guide you down into my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:28.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}And let us pray for the world to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}There is peace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:35.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The truth within us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:38.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Emptiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:41.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Erodes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:47.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Cuz you're free from pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:54.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Future is just too bright to show you ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Wake up now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:00.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}It's time to lead new souls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:07.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Orbit of photon and universe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:13.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}I am just the part of its plan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:20.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}目には見えない歪んだ空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:28.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}人は何処へと歩いていくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:32.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}The last game
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------EDCN---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:13.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}来到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:16.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}拥抱我的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:22.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}让我指引你到我的灵魂深处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:28.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}让我们为世界的苏醒而祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}这里和平而安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:35.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}真理与我们共存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:38.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}无尽的空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:41.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}侵蚀你的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:47.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}因为你从未遭受痛苦与悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.38,0:22:54.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}未来太过刺眼 前路无法看清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.50,0:22:56.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}现在醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:00.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}指引新的灵魂的时刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.82,0:23:07.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}光子与宇宙的运转轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:13.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我只是其中微不足道的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:20.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}双眼看不到的扭曲天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:28.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我该何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:32.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}最后的一场游戏
